      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Soak the<strong> skewers</strong> in <strong>cold water </strong>(this prevents them from burning when cooking)</p><p>Add each <strong>sweetcorn cobette</strong> to a piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and wrap them up tightly until fully sealed</p><p>Put the<strong> sweetcorn cobettes </strong>in the oven for 25 min or until tender and cooked through</p>",
